import './Toggle.css'; function Toggle() { const body = document.querySelector('body'), sidebar = body.querySelector('nav'), toggle = body.querySelector(".toggle"), searchBtn = body.querySelector(".search-box"), modeSwitch = body.querySelector(".toggle-switch"), modeText = body.querySelector(".mode-text"); toggle.addEventListener("click", () => { sidebar.classList.toggle("close"); }) searchBtn.addEventListener("click", () => { sidebar.classList.remove("close"); }) modeSwitch.addEventListener("click", () => { body.classList.toggle("dark"); if (body.classList.contains("dark")) { modeText.innerText = "Light mode"; } else { modeText.innerText = "Dark mode"; } }); return (
